Description: Well, this may be the last Relic Strat Style guitar we do. Gradually fading out all builds but relic teles. So here is what we got. Used Fender Squire body that has been painted Nitro Black over Green, and then sprayed with Gracey's Vintage White, Blonde, and Neck Amber Color to get this beautiful vintage cream look. Not bad if I say so myself. This is the original bridge that came with the guitar. Brand New Maple on Maple neck from Eden Guitars. Brand New Fender Squire 2 Pin Tuners. New Pickguard and Tremelo cover. New Humbucker Strat Style Pickups. These are the China Brand. My Partner has done an excellent job of wiring up these pickups with a Art of the Tone Push/Pull Volume know so you can switch from Single Coil to Full Humbucker on all pickups. The Cavities have been fully Copper shielded. Partner says this baby plays like a dream. We will be posting another video as well soon. 1 Set of Cream 48/50/52mm Dual Coil Pickups For Fender Strat Electric Guitar Description: - Guitar Neck Middle Bridge Humbucker Pickup Set - Fits for Fender, Stratocaster style electric guitars - Resistance: N/M/B: 4.5K/4.5K/9K - Pole spacing: 48/50/52mm- Material: Copper, plastic - Color: Cream If the actual Shipping charges paid do not cover the Priority Shipping I may choose and alternative expedited shipping method of my choosing. ***Kirby Kustoms is in no way affiliated with Fender or Squire Trademarks. All Sales are Final and there are no returns. Please ask any and all questions prior to bidding. This is a relic refurbishment with Scratches, chips, etc. Its meant to be that way. Thanks for looking! Another video will be posted later. This video was for a previous Customer that has not completed this purchase.
